  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nCurrently, when we have a channel (community or not) with unread messages, the chat name is in bold and that's it.\r\nIn the screenshot below, the channel that has a new message is `#testjo`, but it's almosy undistinguishable from the one that's active:\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/11926403/201999197-a4bd07b5-7d8a-4a8e-beea-48371f7c6fb0.png)\r\n \r\nI suggest doing the same as in mobile and add a blue dot next to channels with a new message",
